description: Plan for a grid of size 4x6 with 4 boxes. Each cell has one robot arm. The task is to move each box from its initial cell to its goal cell through a sequence of legal moves. At every time step, a box can either remain in place, move to an adjacent cell, or if it is at its goal cell, be marked as 'goal' and remain there.
